  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hybrid Poisson + Elo model for match outcome prediction",
    "Dynamic Elo ratings updated after each match result",
    "Home advantage calculation based on historical goal difference",
    "Attack and defense strength factors per team (home/away)",
    "Win/draw/loss probability output with expected goals",
    "Parallel Monte Carlo simulation support (10k–100k runs)",
    "Desktop GUI (Tkinter) for interactive match entry and simulation",
    "Markdown output tables ready for reports and posts",
    "CSV data management with append support for new results",
    "xG (expected goals) ranking per club"
